  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join our Discord!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2057840/extras/a5a939f741f53902e685ff53e2645c23.avif?t=1727341738\" width=600 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2024/01/25: v3.0 IS HERE!</strong></h2><ol><li>Localisations for Korean and Chinese (simplified and traditional)!<br></li><li><strong>90+ total charts!</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Around 15 more charts each for Easy and Normal difficulties -- now more beginner friendly!</li></ul></li><li><strong>More than 35 total songs!</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>(New song) Reku Mochizuki “INFiNiTE ENERZY -Overdoze-”<br></li><li>(New song) DJ Kordai “C4”<br></li><li>And loads more EDM! All bops!</li></ul></li><li> <strong>Revamped visuals and UI tweaks!</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Improved visibility of notes and judges!<br></li><li>Visual effects based on your combo!<br></li><li>We have a search bar! Woo!</li></ul></li></ol><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About the game</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2057840/extras/e4e522dc943a4934202c9f86d9ef8c51.poster.avif?t=1727341738\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2057840/extras/e4e522dc943a4934202c9f86d9ef8c51.webm?t=1727341738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2057840/extras/e4e522dc943a4934202c9f86d9ef8c51.mp4?t=1727341738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Click to the beat and track to the bass!</strong> <br><strong>Click notes</strong> - Listen to the beat and watch the ring -- click when it fits the target!<br><strong>Track notes</strong> - Click, hold and track the ball -- keep the crosshair right on target!<br><strong>Track your progress with the stats page and compete on the leaderboard!</strong>",
